          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://cableready.stimulusreflex.com/" class="flex items-center justify-between col-start-2 col-end-4 px-6 py-4 pr-5 mt-4 font-semibold text-purple-600 border-2 border-purple-300 rounded-3xl">
          Read more about CableReady
          <%= image_tag "icons/arrow_circle_right" %>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative grid items-start grid-cols-3 gap-4 -mt-64 top-64">
        <div class="p-8 mt-10 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-3xl">
          <p>
            More responsive screens, simpler code, amazing support.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center mt-6 space-x-4">
            <%= image_tag "people/andrew_cetinic.jpg" %>
            <span>
              <span class="inline-block text-purple-600">Andrew Cetinic</span>
              <span class="inline-block">CEO, <span class="text-purple-600">PeopleForce</span></span>
