          <p>
            What matters is your productivity and how much you enjoy working with a library. I found myself very productive, and I really enjoyed it.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center mt-6 space-x-4">
            <%= image_tag "people/sam_sweeney.jpg" %>
            <span>
              <span class="inline-block text-purple-600">Sam Sweeney</span>
              <span class="inline-block">CEO, <span class="text-purple-600">Trivvy</span></span>
            </span>
          </div>
