            SR saved my day, my (chunky) bacon, my sanity, my dignity, and who knows what else! What a time to be alive!
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center mt-6 space-x-4">
            <%= image_tag "people/trinity_takei.jpg" %>
            <span>
              <span class="inline-block text-purple-600">Trinity Takei</span>
              <span class="inline-block">Lead Developer, <span class="text-purple-600">RCRDSHP</span></span>
            </span>
          </div>
