  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 pt-14 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h3 class="mt-64 mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">
        There are a few cases when StimulusReflex is not the best option
      </h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-20">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold">Offline first</h4>
          <p>
            If your application should work in offline mode, stick with React approach.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold">Games, 3D, AR/VR</h4>
          <p>
            Games and other highly interactive apps are not best fit to StimulusReflex.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold">Your team is mainly front-end</h4>
          <p>
            JS devs may find it hard to learn Rails.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold">
        Subscribe for updates
      </h3>
